### 2. Go Backend (Interface & Nextcloud Adapter)

#### [NEW] [provider.go](file:///c:/Users/meyer/Development/migration/backend/internal/storage/provider.go)
Definiert das provider-agnostische Interface:
```go
package storage

import (
	"context"
	"io"
	"time"
)

type CloudResource struct {
	Path         string    `json:"path"`
	Name         string    `json:"name"`
	Size         int64     `json:"size"`
	IsDir        bool      `json:"is_dir"`
	Hash         string    `json:"hash"`
	LastModified time.Time `json:"last_modified"`
}

type StorageProvider interface {
	Connect(ctx context.Context) (bool, error)
	GetDirectoryListing(ctx context.Context, resourceType, dirPath string) ([]CloudResource, error)
	StreamDownload(ctx context.Context, resourceType, filePath string) (io.ReadCloser, error)
	StreamUpload(ctx context.Context, resourceType, filePath string, stream io.Reader, size int64) error
	StreamUploadChunked(ctx context.Context, resourceType, filePath string, stream io.Reader, size int64, progressChan chan<- int64) error
	FileExists(ctx context.Context, resourceType, filePath string) (bool, int64, error)
	DeleteFile(ctx context.Context, resourceType, filePath string) error
	GetFileHash(ctx context.Context, resourceType, filePath string) (string, error)
	CreateParentDirectories(ctx context.Context, resourceType, filePath string) error
}
```

#### [NEW] [nextcloud.go](file:///c:/Users/meyer/Development/migration/backend/internal/storage/nextcloud.go)
- Implementiert das `StorageProvider`-Interface unter Verwendung der Nextcloud WebDAV/CalDAV/CardDAV-Endpunkte.
- Nutzt die Namespaces:
  - `files` -> `/remote.php/dav/files/{username}/{path}`
  - `calendars` -> `/remote.php/dav/calendars/{username}/{path}` (Erstellung mit `MKCALENDAR`)
  - `contacts` -> `/remote.php/dav/addressbooks/users/{username}/{path}` (Erstellung mit `MKCOL` und CardDAV XML-Body)

#### [NEW] [factory.go](file:///c:/Users/meyer/Development/migration/backend/internal/storage/factory.go)
Erstellt die Adapter-Instanzen basierend auf dem Provider-Typ:
```go
func NewProvider(providerType, urlStr, username, password string) (StorageProvider, error)
```

#### [MODIFY] [processor.go](file:///c:/Users/meyer/Development/migration/backend/internal/processor/processor.go)
- Refactoring, um `storage.StorageProvider` statt des direkten WebDAV-Clients zu nutzen. Alle Transfer-Abläufe verwenden die abstrakten Methoden des Interfaces.

#### [MODIFY] [main.go](file:///c:/Users/meyer/Development/migration/backend/cmd/api/main.go)
- Verwendung der `storage`-Factory zur Instanziierung der Provider.
- Übergabe des angeforderten `resource_type` an die Connect- und Indexierungs-Logik.

